  <div class="content">
    <h2>Grids and columns</h2>

    <p>
      Grids are created using <code>flexbox</code> and flex-* mixins.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h3>Sass mixins</h3>

    <p>The wrapper element uses the <code>flex-row</code> mixin:</p>

    <p><code>@include flex-row($gutter:false);</code></p>

    <p>The column elements use the <code>flex-col</code>Â mixin:</p>

    <p><code>@include flex-col($width, $gutter:false, $grow:0, $shrink:0);</code></p>

    <p>You can take advantage of the <code>span</code> mixin to easily calculate percentage widths, for example:</p>

    <p><code>@include flex-col(span(4,12));</code></p>

    <hr />

    <h3>Gutterless grids</h3>

    <p>By default, grids don't have gutters:</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="grid--row">
    <div class="grid--50">50% column with no gutters</div>
    <div class="grid--50">50% column with no gutters</div>
    <div class="grid--50">50% column with no gutters</div>
    <div class="grid--50">50% column with no gutters</div>
  </div>

  <pre>.grid--row {
  @include flex-row;
}

.grid--50 {
  @include flex-col(50%);
  @include example-column;
}</pre>

  <hr />

  <h3 class="heading-three">Grids with gutters</h3>

  <p>You can pass in a gutter value to the mixins:</p>

  <div>
    <div class="grid-gutter--row">
      <div class="grid-gutter--50">
        <div>50% column with gutters</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--50">
        <div>50% column with gutters</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--50">
        <div>50% column with gutters</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--50">
        <div>50% column with gutters</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <pre>.grid-gutter--row {
  @include flex-row($desktop-gutters);
}

.grid-gutter--50 {
  @include flex-col(50%, $desktop-gutters);
  @include example-column("> div");
}</pre>

  <hr />

  <h3 class="heading-three">Responsive columns</h3>

  <p>These columns have a media query at 800px wide that expands the columns to 50%.</p>

  <div>
    <div class="grid-gutter--row">
      <div class="grid-gutter--25-50">
        <div>25% column with gutters, that responds to 50%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--25-50">
        <div>25% column with gutters, that responds to 50%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--25-50">
        <div>25% column with gutters, that responds to 50%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--25-50">
        <div>25% column with gutters, that responds to 50%</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <pre>.grid-gutter--25-50 {
  @include flex-col(25%, $desktop-gutters);
  @include example-column("> div");
  @include media-query(800px) {
    @include flex-col(50%);
  }
}</pre>

  <hr />

  <h3 class="heading-three">Responsive gutters</h3>

  <p>These grids have flexible gutters:</p>

  <div>
    <div class="grid-gutter--row--responsive">
      <div class="grid-gutter--50--responsive">
        <div>50% column with responsive gutters</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--50--responsive">
        <div>50% column with responsive gutters</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--25-50--responsive">
        <div>25% column with gutters, that responds to 50% with a smaller gutter</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--25-50--responsive">
        <div>25% column with gutters, that responds to 50% with a smaller gutter</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--25-50--responsive">
        <div>25% column with gutters, that responds to 50% with a smaller gutter</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-gutter--25-50--responsive">
        <div>25% column with gutters, that responds to 50% with a smaller gutter</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <pre>.grid-gutter--row--responsive {
  @include flex-row($desktop-gutters);
  @include media-query(800px) {
    @include flex-row($small-gutter);
  }
}
.grid-gutter--50--responsive {
  @include flex-col(50%, $desktop-gutters);
  @include example-column("> div");

  @include media-query(800px) {
    @include flex-col(50%, $small-gutter);
  }
}
.grid-gutter--25-50--responsive {
  @include flex-col(25%, $desktop-gutters);
  @include example-column("> div");

  @include media-query(800px) {
    @include flex-col(50%, $small-gutter);
  }
}</pre>

